 in the systems with lower dark halo to stellar mass\nratio within the optical radius, which, if confirmed, gives evidences of the\neffective radial mixing of gas in galaxies with the relatively light dark\nmatter halo.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 29 Oct 2015 22:08:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-12-16"}
