t the LFQPO peak in the power spectrum is\nbroadened owing to intermittent oscillations with varying frequencies, which\ncould be explained by using the Lense-Thirring precession model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 30 Oct 2015 15:27:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-12-16"}
